      UserOperationLogQuery operationType(String operationType)

    • operationId

      UserOperationLogQuery operationId(String operationId)
      Query entries of a composite operation. This allows grouping multiple updates which are part of the same operation: for instance, a User may update multiple fields of a UserTask when calling TaskService.saveTask(org.cibseven.bpm.engine.task.Task) which will be logged as separate OperationLogEntries with the same 'operationId'
